preference.name: CAEProductViewerDisplayNamePref
preference.preference_description: Stores the internal names of the BOM Line properties whose display names appear as column headings from left-to-right in the Product view of the CAE Manager application. This preference value is only a repository, and it is not to be modified other than by the Product view code in the CAE Manager application.
